long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Get AI-powered insights for any videos. 
The Chrome extension "MB YT-Insights" enhances your YouTube viewing experience by analysing video content to provide actionable insights. It offers engagement scores, highlights key moments, tracks complexity and sentiment, identifies audience matches, and extracts key terms for a deeper understanding of the video's focus, tone, and depthâ€”all displayed conveniently alongside the video.
